    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The intention of this function (1) is not to verify the prove of productivity increase/decrease, but only allow verified other productivity provider contract to call to change. For instance, another staking/unstaking contract. The reason why we propose this interface is for decoupling the interests generation and the productivity providers.\r\n\r\nOne of the most important intention that why we've proposed the productivity rather than the current  share model is because the share model is not count for the time parameter.\r\n\r\nYou could think share model is one of the possible way of providing  productivities. When calculating a user's profit, our algorithm calculates a user's share during a time period compare to a instant snapshot of the share's distribution.\r\n\r\nAlso from what you've mentioned, if a total accumulated interests are 100, and user hold 1% share propotional, there is noway to determine how much he could receive if he constantly calls withdraw.",
